I need something
classic but modern.

75
00:04:00,474 --> 00:04:03,042
Something with drama,
but also understated.

76
00:04:04,044 --> 00:04:07,646
     Um... aren't all those
      things opposites?

77
00:04:08,048 --> 00:04:10,049
     Yes. So?

78
00:04:10,451 --> 00:04:11,850
        But, how can I...

