00:07:38,792 --> 00:07:39,758
              Ahem!

161
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:42,693
      [firm voice] Severe,
     but not unapproachable.

162
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,700
       Acceptable business
          attire.

163
00:07:45,297 --> 00:07:45,964
       [normal soft voice]
          Oh...

164
00:07:46,066 --> 00:07:48,333
      Does that sound like
       a shop pony to you?

