00:08:25,505 --> 00:08:26,471
             [groan]

180
00:08:26,973 --> 00:08:27,539
             [thud]

181
00:08:27,741 --> 00:08:29,841
            [panting]

182
00:08:30,043 --> 00:08:32,311
         Ahh! Smokey Junior!

183
00:08:32,613 --> 00:08:34,379
   I can't believe it worked.

184
00:08:37,117 --> 00:08:38,917
    [snobby voice] I suppose
     clothes really do

